comments: Oladipo (HOU) jumps alongside of Maledon's (OKC) path to the basket and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Tate (HOU) sets the screen on Dort (OKC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
House Jr. (HOU) drives along the baseline and marginal contact occurs with Pokusevski (OKC).  The contact does not affect House Jr.'s ability to make the pass.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Jerome (OKC) throws the pass out of bounds.
Jerome (OKC) makes contact to Wall's (HOU) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Tate (HOU) makes clean contact with the ball when he reaches in during the jump shot by Pokusevski (OKC).
Roby (OKC) and Oladipo (HOU) both go for the rebound and marginal contact occurs as Oladipo taps the ball to Wood (HOU).
Dort (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position and cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt by Wall (HOU).
Tate (HOU) engages with Dort (OKC) and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.  Dort's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Tate (HOU) commits a take foul on Pokusevski (OKC).
